.TH "mipi_dbi_spi_transfer" 9 "mipi_dbi_spi_transfer" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
mipi_dbi_spi_transfer \- SPI transfer helper
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" mipi_dbi_spi_transfer
.BI "(struct spi_device *spi "  ","
.BI "u32 speed_hz "  ","
.BI "u8 bpw "  ","
.BI "const void *buf "  ","
.BI "size_t len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "spi" 12
SPI device
.IP "speed_hz" 12
Override speed (optional)
.IP "bpw" 12
Bits per word
.IP "buf" 12
Buffer to transfer
.IP "len" 12
Buffer length
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This SPI transfer helper breaks up the transfer of \fIbuf\fP into chunks which
the SPI controller driver can handle.
.SH "RETURN"
Zero on success, negative error code on failure.
